reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not a good phone case for an athletic 11 yr old
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this phone case for my 11 year old nephew and from the start it did not pass the muster. First off, my sister in law cracked the screen protector whilst it was in her jacket pocket. This was fine since due to a mis-communication, she purchased the same phone case for him and my wife, lol, he had an extra one. Yet, less than a month later, he broke the case itself and the ring stand broke off as well. His other phone case has been holding up well so far and for that reason I cannot entirely blame the product itself. My nephew is very athletic and he is a boy, lol. So I am rating it a 3 star instead of a lower star rating.
